'               string if it is not zero.
'Methods:       None
'Inputs:        lLineNumber
'Parameters:    None
'Outputs:       None
'Returns:       A string representing the line number
'Errors:        This routine raises no known errors.
'Assumptions:   None
'Updates:
'       Type any updates here.
